data.title: Tesla Model 3 Outsells Vastly Competitors In China For June
data.text: While operations in its Fremont factory were slowed down in the second quarter due to the COVID-19 pandemic, Tesla Inc's (NASDAQ: TSLA) Gigafactory Shanghai kept churning out Model 3s.

data.title: Toni Sacconaghi on why his price target for Tesla is $900
data.text: Toni Sacconaghi, Bernstein senior research analyst, joins 'Squawk Alley' to discuss his $900 Tesla price target and the risks to Tesla's stock.

data.title: Tesla Is Seeing Strong Demand for Its Vehicles
data.text: Even amid a pandemic, order trends for Tesla vehicles are exceeding supply.
